metatags.dc.title: Typescript carrier with firmly held hanger attachment - accommodates clip with groove having projection to retain script during type carriage movements
metatags.dc.description: A typescript support has a suspended or filing attachment fixed to at least one side. A cut-out section in the hanger accommodates a dip device. The cut-out (6) is of larger dimension throughout its length than the thickness of the section (7) it is to accommodate. An inwardly projecting attachment (8,9) is provided which engages in the cut-out (6) under the first edge nearest the side rim (11). The hanger attachment (2) is mounted off-centre and in line with the centre of gravity line (10) of the typescript carrier (1).
